#. [objectives]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:129
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You will learn the basics of:\n"
"Movement\n"
"Attacking\n"
"Healing\n"
"Recruiting"
msgstr ""
"Вы изучите основы:\n"
" движения\n"
" атаки\n"
" лечения\n"
" вербовки"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:131
